                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Look Before You Book</Header>
                <Paragraph>The FMCSA website has resources for those making travel plans and for those looking to charter a bus for a sporting event, field trip, or other group activity. Safety tips and information, software applications (apps) to research bus operators, and information on reporting safety violations are available on the "Look Before You Book" web pages.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
